  <h2>Plan It Early</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Evaluate the site first.</strong> Soil and layout influence the whole plot plan.</li>
    <li><strong>Coordinate the sequence.</strong> The system fits into the construction schedule at the right stage.</li>
    <li><strong>Design for the finished property.</strong> Account for how the home will actually be used.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <p>
    Early evaluation is the theme — it keeps the system from constraining the build after decisions are locked in. See the <a href="/resources/septic-installation-replacement/">installation hub</a>, or <a href="/request-service/">request septic service</a> to begin planning.
  </p>

